Pricacy Policy
This document, referred to as the "Privacy Policy" (hereinafter referred to as the "Policy"), outlines the terms governing the collection and utilization of Personal Information from Users (referred to as "You") by Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERLÂ (referred to as "Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL") during the download, installation, and use of the mobile applications "Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL" (hereinafter referred to as the "Mobile application").
CONSENT OF THE USER:

By downloading, installing, and using the Mobile application, you (also referred to as the "User") voluntarily provide written consent for the processing of your Personal Information as specified in this Policy.

 GENERAL TERMS:

1.1. This Policy constitutes an integral part of the End User License Agreement (EULA) for the Mobile application. By downloading and utilizing the Mobile application, you fully accept the terms outlined in this Policy.

1.2. The methods for processing Personal Information include actions such as collection, recording, systematization, storage, updating, extraction, use, transfer, depersonalization, blocking, deletion, and destruction, with or without automated facilities.

1.3. Terms from the EULA and other agreements with the User are applicable unless explicitly stated otherwise in this Policy.

 PERSONAL INFORMATION:

2.1. When using the Mobile application, the User does not actively provide personal information. Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL does not collect and store data that enables User identification.

2.2. Personal Information, as defined in this Policy, includes the User's email or Instagram account provided during product surveys for users who made purchases in the Mobile application.

2.3. The User acknowledges the use of third-party software in the Mobile application, which may collect and transmit depersonalized data.

THIRD-PARTY SOFTWARE:

Third-party software may encompass analytic systems such as 'Amplitude,' 'Intercom,' 'Appsflyer,' 'Facebook SDK,' and 'Firebase.' The collected data may include device information, query data, and other details of user activity. The collection and use of this data are subject to the respective third-party privacy policies.

CHILDREN'S PRIVACY:

Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL does not intentionally collect personal data from children under 16. If such information is inadvertently obtained, it will be promptly deleted upon discovery.

PURPOSES OF PERSONAL INFORMATION PROCESSING:

Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL may use Personal Information for communication, marketing, statistical research, and targeting advertising based on depersonalized data.

USER'S RIGHTS:

The User has rights to be informed, access, correct, restrict, object, withdraw consent, delete personal data, and receive data for portability. These rights can be exercised by contacting Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL.

DATA RETENTION:

Personal Information will be stored for as long as necessary or permitted by law. Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL periodically reviews data processing systems for relevance.

DATA PROTECTION:

Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL stores and protects Personal Information against unauthorized access according to internal terms and regulations.

TRANSFER OF PERSONAL INFORMATION:

Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL may transfer Personal Information to third parties with User consent, for Mobile application functionality, third-party service providers, or asset transfers.

AMENDMENTS AND DELETION:

For questions, amendments, or deletion requests regarding Personal Information, users can contact Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL at programadorviktor@icloud.com.

AMENDMENTS TO PRIVACY POLICY:

Programacion Viktor Seraleev IERL may unilaterally amend or terminate this Policy without prior notice. Users are advised to regularly check the current version.
